 This package add some hooks to the live installer for supporting
 the extrahooks system.

Package: extrahooks-dev
Architecture: any
Section: devel
Priority: extra
Depends: debhelper, devscripts, make
Description: Utilities for creating extrahooks packages 
 extrahooks is a program for creating your owns extrahooks packages.
 .
 There are also a templates for those packages. And documentation
 about how to create and use them.

